
<p>Reuters <strong><a href="https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/bridgewaters-flagship-fund-was-bearish-us-stocks-rally-fizzled-2023-08-16/">exclusively reported</a></strong> that Bridgewater Associates&#8217; flagship fund had a bearish view on U.S. stocks in late July just as a rally that saw the benchmark S&amp;P 500 soar this year was about to lose steam, according to a presentation to investors seen by Reuters. </p>
